verbose_text: Despite the fact that many of the predicted off-target sites contained as few as two mis-matches (XREF_TABLE, Guide 11.1 and 11.2 and guide 13.1) none of the sequences amplified from the earclip DNA of any of the three founder lines contained any evidence of CAS9 mediated deletions or base pair changes in any of the four most likely predicted off-target sites (XREF_FIG, XREF_FIG).
